title: Welcome Home! 2 bedroom available
posting_body: ['Welcome to Woodway Village where you’ll enjoy worry free living, open & spacious floor plans, private garages and a beautifully landscaped community!', 'Located Along IH-35 Corridor and just a few minutes from Downtown Austin near the towns best dining and shopping areas.', 'Offering a variety of spacious 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartments & townhomes which include large bedrooms with ample closet space, washer and dryer connections, fully equipped kitchens, an attached garage, & ceiling fans in each room!', 'Great news!', 'Water, sewer, & trash services are included!', 'Not only do we have great apartment amenities, but we have great community amenities as well!', 'Enjoy our refreshing outdoor pool & wadding area, on-site laundry, on-site daycare, & outdoor grilling areas.', 'Have a pet?', 'We are a pet-friendly community!', 'We allow up to two pets per apartment home.', 'If you are interested in an apartment home at Woodway Village, call today.', 'TRANSFORMATION UNDERWAY - RENOVATION IN PROGRESS!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Swimming Pool with New Splash Pad', '- Central Air-Conditioning', '- Intrusion Alarm with Alarm System Monitoring Available', '- On-Site Fitness Center', '- 24-Hour Emergency Maintenance Service', '- Picnic & BBQ Areas', '- Pet-Friendly Community', 'We are a pet-friendly community.', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Woodway Village participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $46,380 | 2 Occupants: $52,980 | 3', 'Occupants: $59,580 | 4 Occupants: $66,180 | 5 Occupants: $71,520 | 6 Occupants: $76,800.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community;\xa0credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Tuesday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Thursday-Friday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Call today to learn more about our community:', 'show contact info', 'Woodway Village', '4600 Nuckols Crossing Road', 'Austin, TX, 78744', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', '0xshLR1sl']
